official_title: To direct the Secretary of the Interior to convey to the State of Minnesota the New London National Fish Hatchery production facility.

summary.text: Authorizes the conveyance, without reimbursement, of all U.S. interest in the New London National Fish Hatchery production facility to the State of Minnesota solely for the Minnesota fishery resources management program.

titles.title: To direct the Secretary of the Interior to convey to the State of Minnesota the New London National Fish Hatchery production facility.
